===message:A hiccup is a sudden inspiration of air caused by a spasmodic contraction of the diaphragm while the glottis is closed. The sound is caused by air striking the vocal folds. The reason for hiccups is not well understood, and they seem to have no apparent useful function. 
=========yorg=========
